Class ToolNumberAdapter<C extends ToolNumber>

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Number
      • tools.numbers.ToolNumber

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, PublicCloneable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ComplexNumber
    @Deprecated
public abstract class ToolNumberAdapter<C extends ToolNumber>
extends ToolNumber
    Deprecated.
    Old class, and needs to be refactored.
    This decorator converts each input number to a default ToolNumber using the convert function. Note that this must be an instance of C.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
